{"tid":1633031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我地真係需要去檢討再作戰","createTime":"2019-10-07T02:01:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T02:40:26.000Z","uid":242158,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7b179c97db711fd05c215aa08c3c8d82e9e138df","tid":1633031,"uid":242158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:01:10.000Z","msg":"今日真係唔可以再重複10.4嘅錯<br />\n我明白大家都好嬲我都係<br />\n但唔係想分化 而係10.4之後國際聲音大家有目共睹<br />\n就連最基本好多中立嘅都開始怪我地 呢兩日不斷出現抱怨聲明<br />\n企出黎係需要嘅 但會唔會呢排停一停爆先和理非出黎？<br />\n<br />\n讚唔讚成都好 希望大家可以表態等大家有共識"},{"pid":"32ac113c460728c60f54ee46409a12863f9e087c","tid":1633031,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:01:58.000Z","msg":"明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3fy6PwF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3fy6PwF.png&h=ea9a012e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyYDlCk4w_-I&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4mlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=9a9faa5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I</a><br />\n<br />\n關於民權法，要講清楚，美國並不要求大家和平<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632886\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632886</a><br />\n<br />\n「戰略」搏一個星期，我地可以贏一世<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630040</a>"},{"pid":"f1ec553a1a432c03e2c4a2320854e5efafa52d5a","tid":1633031,"uid":33984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:03:04.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"c2b958345e06de17a69c24f50ad96d0d2fcad83b","tid":1633031,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:05:20.000Z","msg":"我有新計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br